lead_paragraph: As Tiger Woods prepares for what many pundits believe to be the final chapter of his competitive career, it is fair to say that the crystal ball detailing what lies ahead for him is totally opaque at this point.

headline.print_headline: No Clear View Ahead for Tiger on PGA Tour Return
